gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "You are conscious.\n"
	.string "This is an improvement.\p"
	.string "I am a Miss Nanny unit assigned\n"
	.string "to the Vault 42 Medical Bay.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "You were brought in approximately\n"
	.string "four hours ago in a condition\l"
	.string "I would describe as... bad.\p"
	.string "You were hit by a door.\p"
	.string "Specifically, by someone opening\n"
	.string "it into your face.\p"
	.string "Protocol requires that I conduct a\n"
	.string "cognitive evaluation before\l"
	.string "clearing you for discharge.\p"
	.string "I will ask you some questions.\n"
	.string "Please answer honestly.\l"
	.string "I will know if you do not.\p"
	.string "That last part was not true.\n"
	.string "I cannot detect dishonesty.\p"
	.string "But it does make things more\n"
	.string "efficient if you are truthful.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_RememberQuestion::
	.string "First question. Do you know the\n"
	.string "basics of where and when you are?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_RemindResponse::
	.string "In 2077, the United States and China\n"
	.string "engaged in a brief but productive\l"
	.string "nuclear exchange.\p"
	.string "This is commonly referred to\n"
	.string "as the Great War.\p"
	.string "Vault-Tec, in its infinite wisdom,\n"
	.string "anticipated this outcome.\p"
	.string "Vault 42 is one of many underground\n"
	.string "residential facilities built to\l"
	.string "preserve humankind.\p"
	.string "Outside these walls lies the\n"
	.string "Chicago metropolitan area.\p"
	.string "It is, technically, still there but...\n"
	.string "you are not missing anything.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_RememberResponse::
	.string "Good.\n"
	.string "That is one less concern.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_YearQuestion::
	.string "Second question. More specifically...\n"
	.string "What year is it?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_YearWrong::
	.string "That is not correct.\n"
	.string "I will note this in your file.\p"
	.string "Some memories do not come back.\n"
	.string "It is better not to dwell.\p"
	.string "The current year is 2291.\n"
	.string "214 years since the Great War.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_YearCorrect::
	.string "Correct.\n"
	.string "214 years since the Great War.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "Now I need to evaluate your\n"
	.string "self-perception.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "What is your gender presentation?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_HairColor::
	.string "Next, what is your hair color?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_SkinTone::
	.string "And last, what is your complexion?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_Confirm::
	.string "Confirm?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_FaceComment::
	.string "Oh! I see... Well...\n"
	.string "I should note, you have some bruising.\p"
	.string "And some swelling.\p"
	.string "And some additional bruising\n"
	.string "around the swelling.\p"
	.string "Your face should return to normal...\n"
	.string "Eventually...\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
	.string "Moving on...\n"
	.string "Do you remember your name?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
	.string "And you are certain it's {PLAYER}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "Your classmate found you on the floor\n"
	.string "and carried you here.\p"
	.string "Can you recall their name?\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_ToddCorrect::
	.string "Correct.\n"
	.string "Your memory is improving.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_MissNanny_ToddWrong::
	.string "That is not correct.\n"
	.string "His name is Todd.\p"
	.string "You did not remember the person\n"
	.string "who may have saved your life.\p"
	.string "I will note this in your file.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "All right, are you ready?\p"
	.string "Your very own adventure is about\n"
	.string "to unfold.\p"
	.string "Take courage, and leap into the\n"
	.string "world of POKéMON where dreams,\l"
	.string "adventure, and friendships await!\p"
	.string "Well, I'll be expecting you later.\n"
	.string "Come see me in my POKéMON LAB.\p"
	.string "$"
